snippet.title: Dr. Finklestein's Marvelous Room - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
STORE PAGE: https://devbeef.com/buy/dfmr
DISCORD: https://devbeef.com/discord

Dr. Finklestein's Marvelous Room is a community run experimental story game. With the end of the world fast approaching, Dr. Gumphrey Finklestein announces his plans for a groundbreaking scientific experiment. What will it entail? Does even he know?
